<Q REND="inline">Come, my fellow &s;oldiers, &s;ays he, <HI>lets us
dine chear|fully here, for to-night we &s;hall &s;up with Pluto.</HI></Q> His
men upon hearing his determined pur|po&s;e, &s;et up a loud &s;hout, as if they
